-- Deutsche Bank's CEO Ackermann Says Worst of Euro-Region Crisis Is Now Past
-- Juan Pablo Spinetto
-- 2010-06-18T12:27:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-18/deutsche-bank-s-ceo-ackermann-says-worst-of-euro-region-crisis-is-now-past.html

          
          
              Deutsche Bank AG Chief Executive
Officer Josef Ackermann said today that the worst of the euro
crisis “is behind us.”  
 Ackermann was speaking in an interview with Bloomberg
Television at the St. Petersburg International Economic Forum in
Russia.  
